1
00:00:44,430 --> 00:00:47,600
My lord, don't you think Gu Shanhe is acting a bit strangely today?

2
00:00:47,600 --> 00:00:48,730
You entered the tent as the army inspector,

3
00:00:48,730 --> 00:00:49,730
yet he didn't even offer you a seat.

4
00:00:49,730 --> 00:00:50,630
It seems disrespectful.

5
00:00:50,630 --> 00:00:52,490
Could he have noticed something?

6
00:00:52,500 --> 00:00:53,500
Noticed what?

7
00:00:54,060 --> 00:00:55,590
What could he have noticed?

8
00:00:55,660 --> 00:00:57,500
The enemy army is right at our doorstep.

9
00:00:57,500 --> 00:00:59,530
Does he have the mind to think about anything else?

10
00:00:59,530 --> 00:01:01,130
There's always a reason for abnormal behavior.

11
00:01:01,130 --> 00:01:03,230
Whenever I see that Xue Gai, I feel like nothing good will happen.

12
00:01:03,230 --> 00:01:06,060
Don't you feel that Gu Shanhe is protecting him at every turn now?

13
00:01:06,060 --> 00:01:06,860
Xue Gai.

14
00:01:06,960 --> 00:01:09,289
Are you sure he is the current Taishiling?

15
00:01:10,560 --> 00:01:12,530
It's easy to look alike, but hard to capture the spirit.

16
00:01:12,530 --> 00:01:14,330
Should I go back and check his background?

17
00:01:14,330 --> 00:01:17,330
Check? Even if you go back to the capital and find out he is Shen Wenyuan, so what?

18
00:01:17,330 --> 00:01:17,860
By the time you get back,

19
00:01:17,860 --> 00:01:19,060
the war will be over.

20
00:01:19,060 --> 00:01:19,930
True.

21
00:01:20,300 --> 00:01:21,730
He'll die here sooner or later.

22
00:01:21,730 --> 00:01:23,430
But we can't just let it go, can we?

23
00:01:23,430 --> 00:01:25,830
I'm the one who decides whether to let it go.

24
00:01:31,260 --> 00:01:33,360
You brute, are you rushing to die?

25
00:01:46,229 --> 00:01:47,759
Why didn't you kill him too?

26
00:01:49,930 --> 00:01:51,930
I kept him alive for a great purpose.

27
00:01:52,500 --> 00:01:56,229
Haha, sir, your actions are truly unfathomable.

28
00:02:03,830 --> 00:02:05,000
I'm busy with military affairs

29
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:06,260
and couldn't get away.

30
00:02:06,300 --> 00:02:07,830
Oh, why are you so late?

31
00:02:08,130 --> 00:02:09,699
I came out of the central tent,

32
00:02:09,699 --> 00:02:12,960
and the clerk beside me was killed right in front of my eyes.

33
00:02:13,100 --> 00:02:13,700
I saw it.

34
00:02:13,760 --> 00:02:16,020
The one who just killed him was Gu Shanhe.

35
00:02:16,860 --> 00:02:17,860
Was it really him?

36
00:02:19,200 --> 00:02:20,329
Absolutely.

37
00:02:27,160 --> 00:02:28,160
You brute,

38
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,660
are you rushing to die?

39
00:02:31,230 --> 00:02:32,400
A mere clerk

40
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:35,200
is worth Gu Shanhe doing it himself?

41
00:02:35,829 --> 00:02:37,560
And he killed him instead of me.

42
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:38,360
Why is that?

43
00:02:39,030 --> 00:02:40,460
There's only one possibility.

44
00:02:40,460 --> 00:02:43,790
Xue Gai in the tent is the current Taishiling, Shen Wenyuan.

45
00:02:45,760 --> 00:02:47,160
Gu Shanhe is suspicious.

46
00:02:47,160 --> 00:02:48,500
They are guarding the perimeter closely.

47
00:02:48,500 --> 00:02:49,660
No news can get out.

48
00:02:49,930 --> 00:02:52,500
Please use this matter to distract them in the main tent.

49
00:02:52,500 --> 00:02:53,829
I'll find a way to get out of the camp and report.

50
00:02:53,829 --> 00:02:57,430
The generals here are all Gu Shanhe's trusted men. If you leave,

51
00:02:58,460 --> 00:02:59,600
leaving me alone,

52
00:02:59,660 --> 00:03:00,960
how can I escape?

53
00:03:01,460 --> 00:03:03,030
Since Gu Shanhe didn't kill you,

54
00:03:03,030 --> 00:03:04,500
it means you are still useful.

55
00:03:04,500 --> 00:03:05,300
Once I get out,

56
00:03:05,430 --> 00:03:06,700
the army will break through the camp in an instant.

57
00:03:06,700 --> 00:03:08,830
I will naturally find a way to save you.

58
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:18,260
Report! Great victory at Gunshi Gorge!

59
00:03:18,260 --> 00:03:20,300
Commandant Chen is already on his way back.

60
00:03:20,300 --> 00:03:23,160
Everything went exactly as Brother Wenyuan predicted.

61
00:03:23,160 --> 00:03:25,220
Then it's time for me to make a choice.

62
00:03:28,530 --> 00:03:29,329
Hmm.

63
00:03:54,100 --> 00:03:55,630
The army is approaching Gu Shanhe's troops of the Sheng Army.

64
00:03:55,630 --> 00:03:57,160
They are less than fifty miles away.

65
00:03:57,160 --> 00:03:57,960
Gu Shanhe.

66
00:03:58,360 --> 00:03:59,760
Li Zhantian's grandson.

67
00:04:00,130 --> 00:04:03,000
Whose land can 5,000 rats from Mobei protect?

68
00:04:03,630 --> 00:04:05,430
Drive them to Duanren Mountain.

69
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:09,960
The women of the Great Sheng Dynasty

70
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:13,060
are indeed charming and enchanting.

71
00:04:24,300 --> 00:04:25,400
You dance terribly,

72
00:04:25,400 --> 00:04:26,700
and you're not much better with a knife.

73
00:04:26,700 --> 00:04:28,530
You're from the Sand Fox tribe, aren't you?

74
00:04:28,530 --> 00:04:29,530
Why try to kill me?

75
00:04:31,300 --> 00:04:33,630
Since you know I'm from the Sand Fox tribe,

76
00:04:34,030 --> 00:04:35,159
you should also know

77
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:37,030
that you killed my whole family.

78
00:04:37,030 --> 00:04:38,030
I want revenge!

79
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:39,460
Throw her into my tent.

80
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:41,220
I will punish her personally.

81
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:43,430
No wonder you look so familiar.

82
00:04:44,430 --> 00:04:45,960
You must be Jin Wu's sister.

83
00:04:46,900 --> 00:04:49,030
Since your sisters are alive and well,

84
00:04:49,200 --> 00:04:51,230
I didn't kill your whole family.

85
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:53,860
Come, continue dancing for me.

86
00:04:54,930 --> 00:04:55,659
Ashina,

87
00:04:56,230 --> 00:04:57,230
Screw your dance!

88
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:01,490
Hmph.

89
00:05:03,400 --> 00:05:05,560
Hahaha.

90
00:05:06,030 --> 00:05:07,330
Kill me if you dare!

91
00:05:07,460 --> 00:05:09,830
You have the same temper as your sister.

92
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:12,060
It's good that you aren't dancing.

93
00:05:12,060 --> 00:05:13,660
At least you know your limits.

94
00:05:13,660 --> 00:05:16,730
Even at my worst, I dance a million times better than you!

95
00:05:16,730 --> 00:05:17,530
Let her go.

96
00:05:29,030 --> 00:05:30,360
I have fought battles all my life.

97
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:31,030
I've roamed far and wide,

98
00:05:31,030 --> 00:05:32,200
and never met my match.

99
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:34,260
I've killed countless people.

100
00:05:34,500 --> 00:05:35,930
It's only natural you want revenge.

101
00:05:35,930 --> 00:05:38,730
It's perfectly justified that you want to kill me.

102
00:05:39,130 --> 00:05:41,730
Give this sheep a fast horse and let her go.

103
00:05:42,330 --> 00:05:43,130
Hmph.

104
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:44,230
Keep your word.

105
00:05:44,460 --> 00:05:44,830
But,

106
00:05:45,760 --> 00:05:46,960
whoever catches her,

107
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:47,930
gets to keep her.

108
00:05:51,460 --> 00:05:53,730
Ashina, you are a bastard!

109
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:55,130
You broke your word!

110
00:05:55,460 --> 00:05:58,390
I curse your entire family to die for 18 generations!

111
00:06:05,330 --> 00:06:07,600
Military report from Gunshi Gorge.

112
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:09,460
Our supplies were burned.

113
00:06:09,730 --> 00:06:11,430
Should we delay the march?

114
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:13,600
That little amount of provisions is nothing.

115
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:15,400
Everything proceeds as planned.

116
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:16,430
Pass down the order.

117
00:06:16,430 --> 00:06:17,490
The army moves out.

118
00:06:28,460 --> 00:06:29,860
What's our next move?

119
00:06:31,130 --> 00:06:32,990
Please advise, Brother Wenyuan.

120
00:06:33,260 --> 00:06:35,659
We can't defend, retreat, or fight.

121
00:06:35,960 --> 00:06:38,500
Five thousand against eighty thousand. The odds are slim.

122
00:06:38,500 --> 00:06:40,159
But if history remains unchanged,

123
00:06:40,159 --> 00:06:42,330
I can predict every wave of the Canglang army's attack.

124
00:06:42,330 --> 00:06:43,430
I also know where the water is,

125
00:06:43,430 --> 00:06:45,230
and when the arrows will run out.

126
00:06:45,960 --> 00:06:47,690
Your presence here won't help.

127
00:06:48,200 --> 00:06:51,200
But a commander leaving the camp is a capital offense.

128
00:06:52,330 --> 00:06:52,930
Actually,

129
00:06:53,400 --> 00:06:54,600
death to me

130
00:06:54,760 --> 00:06:56,460
is better than having my whole family executed.

131
00:06:56,460 --> 00:06:58,500
Besides, staying means death anyway.

132
00:06:58,500 --> 00:06:59,960
Your feud with General Tie

133
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:01,860
started when he felt ashamed to be your backup,

134
00:07:01,860 --> 00:07:03,330
and ended with his lack of support.

135
00:07:03,330 --> 00:07:06,200
No one else's words can untie this knot better than you talking to him in person.

136
00:07:06,200 --> 00:07:07,400
In the eyes of history,

137
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:08,530
he will be known as a general who refused to help,

138
00:07:08,530 --> 00:07:09,990
and trapped his comrades.

139
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:11,300
If resolved,

140
00:07:11,300 --> 00:07:13,400
you both will be the star generals of Dasheng.

141
00:07:13,400 --> 00:07:15,530
I'll leave the seal and military tally to you two.

142
00:07:15,530 --> 00:07:16,660
I'm setting off now.

143
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:19,500
The eight-day bloody battle

144
00:07:19,500 --> 00:07:20,400
is already written in history.

145
00:07:20,400 --> 00:07:22,100
But I can control the limits.

146
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:24,860
Rest assured and go forge a way out for us.

147
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:25,930
If I can't hold it,

148
00:07:25,930 --> 00:07:29,000
I will lead the remaining troops to the Beiyin Mountain gorge.

149
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:31,830
You can lead the reinforcements to meet me there.

150
00:07:44,060 --> 00:07:44,860
Take care.

151
00:07:54,200 --> 00:07:55,000
Take care.

152
00:07:59,060 --> 00:08:00,630
Never speak of wasted ambitions.
